{"tid":436374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[養商家是必須］陳帆指年輕人買不到樓轉買車！","createTime":"2017-10-15T06:08:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-15T14:37:39.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"22d47b32c4a2128aba64ea7e182f8fea05201b60","tid":436374,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T06:08:05.000Z","msg":"陳帆指，現今年輕人的思考模式與他的一代有不同，他認為年輕人買不到樓，但亦想有私人空間時，「讓自己的靈魂從軀體中出來遊走一下」，轉為買車。他認為當中不涉及對與錯，在接載老人家、小孩方面，有車是能夠方便一點，讓未來私家車增長能理性一點，在最後始考慮是否需要增加首次登記稅。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/港聞/125952/陳帆指年輕人買不到樓轉買車-好讓自己的靈魂遊走一下\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2F125952%2F%E9%99%B3%E5%B8%86%E6%8C%87%E5%B9%B4%E8%BC%95%E4%BA%BA%E8%B2%B7%E4%B8%8D%E5%88%B0%E6%A8%93%E8%BD%89%E8%B2%B7%E8%BB%8A-%E5%A5%BD%E8%AE%93%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E9%9D%88%E9%AD%82%E9%81%8A%E8%B5%B0%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%8B&d=AJjNPnWE8cCgUQ5hfbMKxAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=a5d7d906\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/港聞/125952/陳帆指年輕人買不到樓轉買車-好讓自己的靈魂遊走一下</a>"},{"pid":"30aac681b3da04c8c80aaadb9b7e7fc55f63d301","tid":436374,"uid":19454,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T06:09:47.000Z","msg":"一定要把樍蓄花光：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n富：供樓<br />\n<br />\n窮：買車<br />\n<br />\n不容許不花錢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3700287279be3136a6dca0a130975eee487b63d8","tid":436374,"uid":131245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T06:10:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一定要把樍蓄花光：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n富：供樓<br />\n<br />\n窮：買車<br />\n<br />\n不容許不花錢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔花錢就草錢"},{"pid":"a3a20ca8ba5b4e2e4b2f6b38e07f3136d12125e8","tid":436374,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T06:12:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一定要把樍蓄花光：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n富：供樓<br />\n<br />\n窮：買車<br />\n<br />\n不容許不花錢！<img src=\"/